OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FQuite cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fsome rain. Variable amounts of cloud
OL,7,Fand sunny spells in the afternoon
OL,8,Falong with scattered slow moving
OL,9,Fshowers, occasionally heavy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPartly cloudy this evening
OL,12,Fwith any remaining heavy showers soon
OL,13,Fclearing away. The rest of the night
OL,14,Fwill then be largely dry with clear
OL,15,Fspells and light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
