OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA mainly dry and bright
OL,6,Fday. Turning cloudier through the
OL,7,Fafternoon with some patchy rain
OL,8,Farriving later, possible heavy for a
OL,9,Ftime in the evening. Freshening
OL,10,Fafternoon winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FMainly dry, bright and breezy during
OL,14,Fthis period. Some sunny spells,
OL,15,Fperhaps the odd light shower in the
OL,16,Fwest at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
